{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Lymv7uWjuF8XVsKoNi1C4j","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_017qcpKNmqemk4xtzixngxui","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Read Excel sheets for memo data","subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt":"Read the following sheets from the Excel workbook at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx:\n\n1. \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - read all data\n2. \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet - read all data including cell A1\n3. \"CEOCFO Recommendations\" sheet - read all data including cells A1, A2, A3\n\nUse a Node.js script with the xlsx library to read these sheets. Output ALL cell values including A1, A2, A3 for CEOCFO Recommendations, and ALL content from the other sheets.\n\nRun this script:\n```javascript\nconst XLSX = require('xlsx');\nconst path = 'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx';\nconst wb = XLSX.readFile(path);\n\n// Read Vendor Analysis Assessment\nconsole.log('=== VENDOR ANALYSIS ASSESSMENT ===');\nconst vaa = wb.Sheets['Vendor Analysis Assessment'];\nif (vaa) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(vaa, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  data.forEach((row, i) => console.log(`Row ${i+1}:`, JSON.stringify(row)));\n} else {\n  console.log('Sheet not found. Available sheets:', wb.SheetNames);\n}\n\n// Read Top 3 Opportunities\nconsole.log('\\n=== TOP 3 OPPORTUNITIES ===');\nconst t3 = wb.Sheets['Top 3 Opportunities'];\nif (t3) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(t3, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  data.forEach((row, i) => console.log(`Row ${i+1}:`, JSON.stringify(row)));\n  // Also show raw cell A1\n  console.log('A1 raw:', JSON.stringify(t3['A1']));\n} else {\n  console.log('Sheet not found');\n}\n\n// Read CEOCFO Recommendations\nconsole.log('\\n=== CEOCFO RECOMMENDATIONS ===');\nconst ceo = wb.Sheets['CEOCFO Recommendations'];\nif (ceo) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(ceo, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  data.forEach((row, i) => console.log(`Row ${i+1}:`, JSON.stringify(row)));\n  console.log('A1 raw:', JSON.stringify(ceo['A1']));\n  console.log('A2 raw:', JSON.stringify(ceo['A2']));\n  console.log('A3 raw:', JSON.stringify(ceo['A3']));\n} else {\n  console.log('Sheet not found');\n}\n```\n\nRun with: node -e \"<script>\" from C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/\n\nReturn the complete output."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":10606,"cache_read_input_tokens":6212,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":10606,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d2abd3ed-573c-41f0-9505-cb2e0fcd9d65","uuid":"662f7d77-91c3-4c71-be47-6855e51d809b"}
{"type":"system","subtype":"task_started","task_id":"a653ac60f1f42a5cf","tool_use_id":"toolu_017qcpKNmqemk4xtzixngxui","description":"Read Excel sheets for memo data","task_type":"local_agent","prompt":"Read the following sheets from the Excel workbook at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx:\n\n1. \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - read all data\n2. \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet - read all data including cell A1\n3. \"CEOCFO Recommendations\" sheet - read all data including cells A1, A2, A3\n\nUse a Node.js script with the xlsx library to read these sheets. Output ALL cell values including A1, A2, A3 for CEOCFO Recommendations, and ALL content from the other sheets.\n\nRun this script:\n```javascript\nconst XLSX = require('xlsx');\nconst path = 'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx';\nconst wb = XLSX.readFile(path);\n\n// Read Vendor Analysis Assessment\nconsole.log('=== VENDOR ANALYSIS ASSESSMENT ===');\nconst vaa = wb.Sheets['Vendor Analysis Assessment'];\nif (vaa) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(vaa, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  data.forEach((row, i) => console.log(`Row ${i+1}:`, JSON.stringify(row)));\n} else {\n  console.log('Sheet not found. Available sheets:', wb.SheetNames);\n}\n\n// Read Top 3 Opportunities\nconsole.log('\\n=== TOP 3 OPPORTUNITIES ===');\nconst t3 = wb.Sheets['Top 3 Opportunities'];\nif (t3) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(t3, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  data.forEach((row, i) => console.log(`Row ${i+1}:`, JSON.stringify(row)));\n  // Also show raw cell A1\n  console.log('A1 raw:', JSON.stringify(t3['A1']));\n} else {\n  console.log('Sheet not found');\n}\n\n// Read CEOCFO Recommendations\nconsole.log('\\n=== CEOCFO RECOMMENDATIONS ===');\nconst ceo = wb.Sheets['CEOCFO Recommendations'];\nif (ceo) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(ceo, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  data.forEach((row, i) => console.log(`Row ${i+1}:`, JSON.stringify(row)));\n  console.log('A1 raw:', JSON.stringify(ceo['A1']));\n  console.log('A2 raw:', JSON.stringify(ceo['A2']));\n  console.log('A3 raw:', JSON.stringify(ceo['A3']));\n} else {\n  console.log('Sheet not found');\n}\n```\n\nRun with: node -e \"<script>\" from C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/\n\nReturn the complete output.","uuid":"457c3d57-2991-4e55-96e0-30047ad72107","session_id":"d2abd3ed-573c-41f0-9505-cb2e0fcd9d65"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Read the following sheets from the Excel workbook at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx:\n\n1. \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - read all data\n2. \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet - read all data including cell A1\n3. \"CEOCFO Recommendations\" sheet - read all data including cells A1, A2, A3\n\nUse a Node.js script with the xlsx library to read these sheets. Output ALL cell values including A1, A2, A3 for CEOCFO Recommendations, and ALL content from the other sheets.\n\nRun this script:\n```javascript\nconst XLSX = require('xlsx');\nconst path = 'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx';\nconst wb = XLSX.readFile(path);\n\n// Read Vendor Analysis Assessment\nconsole.log('=== VENDOR ANALYSIS ASSESSMENT ===');\nconst vaa = wb.Sheets['Vendor Analysis Assessment'];\nif (vaa) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(vaa, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  data.forEach((row, i) => console.log(`Row ${i+1}:`, JSON.stringify(row)));\n} else {\n  console.log('Sheet not found. Available sheets:', wb.SheetNames);\n}\n\n// Read Top 3 Opportunities\nconsole.log('\\n=== TOP 3 OPPORTUNITIES ===');\nconst t3 = wb.Sheets['Top 3 Opportunities'];\nif (t3) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(t3, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  data.forEach((row, i) => console.log(`Row ${i+1}:`, JSON.stringify(row)));\n  // Also show raw cell A1\n  console.log('A1 raw:', JSON.stringify(t3['A1']));\n} else {\n  console.log('Sheet not found');\n}\n\n// Read CEOCFO Recommendations\nconsole.log('\\n=== CEOCFO RECOMMENDATIONS ===');\nconst ceo = wb.Sheets['CEOCFO Recommendations'];\nif (ceo) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(ceo, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  data.forEach((row, i) => console.log(`Row ${i+1}:`, JSON.stringify(row)));\n  console.log('A1 raw:', JSON.stringify(ceo['A1']));\n  console.log('A2 raw:', JSON.stringify(ceo['A2']));\n  console.log('A3 raw:', JSON.stringify(ceo['A3']));\n} else {\n  console.log('Sheet not found');\n}\n```\n\nRun with: node -e \"<script>\" from C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/\n\nReturn the complete output."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_017qcpKNmqemk4xtzixngxui","session_id":"d2abd3ed-573c-41f0-9505-cb2e0fcd9d65","uuid":"b15fa829-f30d-4cf1-b023-45f82ec8e6c7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T18:44:44.923Z"}
