{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017qcpKNmqemk4xtzixngxui","type":"tool_result","content":"<persisted-output>\nOutput too large (50.8KB). Full output saved to: C:\\Users\\rjega\\.claude\\projects\\C--Users-rjega-vendor-spend-analysis\\d2abd3ed-573c-41f0-9505-cb2e0fcd9d65\\tool-results\\toolu_017qcpKNmqemk4xtzixngxui.json\n\nPreview (first 2KB):\n[\n  {\n    \"type\": \"text\",\n    \"text\": \"Here is the complete output from all three sheets:\\n\\n---\\n\\n## === VENDOR ANALYSIS ASSESSMENT ===\\n\\n**Headers (Row 1):** `Vendor Name | Department | Last 12 months Cost (USD) | 1-line Description on what the Vendor does | Suggestions (Consolidate / Terminate / Optimize costs) | DERIVED-Spend Category`\\n\\n**Data rows 2–387 (386 vendors), all with the same 5-column structure:**\\n\\n| Row | Vendor Name | Department | Cost (USD) | Description | Suggestion |\\n|-----|-------------|------------|------------|-------------|------------|\\n| 2 | (Blank) | G&A | 137.30 | Unidentified vendor with no name or clear purpose | Terminate |\\n| 3 | 4I Advisory Services | Professional Services | 71,860.34 | Management advisory firm providing strategic consulting services | Consolidate |\\n| 4 | 4I Management Consulting Private Limited | Professional Services | 12,117.49 | Management consulting firm overlapping with 4I Advisory Services | Consolidate |\\n| 5 | 4Imprint Direct Ltd | Marketing | 2,436.14 | Promotional merchandise supplier for branded marketing materials | Terminate |\\n| 6 | 6Sense Insights Inc | Marketing | 75.56 | AI-powered revenue intelligence platform for B2B marketing | Terminate |\\n| 7 | Acclime Corporate Services | G&A | 5,412.87 | Corporate services provider for entity management and compliance | Consolidate |\\n| 8 | Acclime Usa, Inc | G&A | 4,994.98 | US entity of Acclime providing corporate administration services | Consolidate |\\n| 9 | Accutrainee Limited | Professional Services | 38,840.80 | Graduate trainee recruitment and placement services | Terminate |\\n| 10 | Adamma Info Services Private Limited | G&A | 273.33 | Back-office information services provider | Terminate |\\n| 11 | Adobe Systems Software | SaaS | 3,928.65 | Creative software suite for design and document management | Terminate |\\n| 12 | Advena | G&A | 153.89 | Unknown vendor with negligible spend and unclear purpose | Terminate |\\n| 13 | Aetna Life And Casual\n...\n</persisted-output>"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d2abd3ed-573c-41f0-9505-cb2e0fcd9d65","uuid":"e591da3c-8ac8-4191-a305-6ac8198bcefd","timestamp":"2026-03-22T18:50:32.927Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the following sheets from the Excel workbook at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx:\n\n1. \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - read all data\n2. \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet - read all data including cell A1\n3. \"CEOCFO Recommendations\" sheet - read all data including cells A1, A2, A3\n\nUse a Node.js script with the xlsx library to read these sheets. Output ALL cell values including A1, A2, A3 for CEOCFO Recommendations, and ALL content from the other sheets.\n\nRun this script:\n```javascript\nconst XLSX = require('xlsx');\nconst path = 'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx';\nconst wb = XLSX.readFile(path);\n\n// Read Vendor Analysis Assessment\nconsole.log('=== VENDOR ANALYSIS ASSESSMENT ===');\nconst vaa = wb.Sheets['Vendor Analysis Assessment'];\nif (vaa) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(vaa, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  data.forEach((row, i) => console.log(`Row ${i+1}:`, JSON.stringify(row)));\n} else {\n  console.log('Sheet not found. Available sheets:', wb.SheetNames);\n}\n\n// Read Top 3 Opportunities\nconsole.log('\\n=== TOP 3 OPPORTUNITIES ===');\nconst t3 = wb.Sheets['Top 3 Opportunities'];\nif (t3) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(t3, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  data.forEach((row, i) => console.log(`Row ${i+1}:`, JSON.stringify(row)));\n  // Also show raw cell A1\n  console.log('A1 raw:', JSON.stringify(t3['A1']));\n} else {\n  console.log('Sheet not found');\n}\n\n// Read CEOCFO Recommendations\nconsole.log('\\n=== CEOCFO RECOMMENDATIONS ===');\nconst ceo = wb.Sheets['CEOCFO Recommendations'];\nif (ceo) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(ceo, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  data.forEach((row, i) => console.log(`Row ${i+1}:`, JSON.stringify(row)));\n  console.log('A1 raw:', JSON.stringify(ceo['A1']));\n  console.log('A2 raw:', JSON.stringify(ceo['A2']));\n  console.log('A3 raw:', JSON.stringify(ceo['A3']));\n} else {\n  console.log('Sheet not found');\n}\n```\n\nRun with: node -e \"<script>\" from C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/\n\nReturn the complete output.","agentId":"a653ac60f1f42a5cf","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here is the complete output from all three sheets:\n\n---\n\n## === VENDOR ANALYSIS ASSESSMENT ===\n\n**Headers (Row 1):** `Vendor Name | Department | Last 12 months Cost (USD) | 1-line Description on what the Vendor does | Suggestions (Consolidate / Terminate / Optimize costs) | DERIVED-Spend Category`\n\n**Data rows 2–387 (386 vendors), all with the same 5-column structure:**\n\n| Row | Vendor Name | Department | Cost (USD) | Description | Suggestion |\n|-----|-------------|------------|------------|-------------|------------|\n| 2 | (Blank) | G&A | 137.30 | Unidentified vendor with no name or clear purpose | Terminate |\n| 3 | 4I Advisory Services | Professional Services | 71,860.34 | Management advisory firm providing strategic consulting services | Consolidate |\n| 4 | 4I Management Consulting Private Limited | Professional Services | 12,117.49 | Management consulting firm overlapping with 4I Advisory Services | Consolidate |\n| 5 | 4Imprint Direct Ltd | Marketing | 2,436.14 | Promotional merchandise supplier for branded marketing materials | Terminate 