eak clauses before issuing termination notices\\n\\nRecommended next step: Assign procurement lead to initiate Salesforce UK renegotiation by 30 April 2026, while simultaneously activating the 265-vendor termination program in Week 1 to capture quick-win savings in parallel.\";\n\nconst cellAddr = XLSX.utils.encode_cell({r: 2, c: 0}); // A3 (0-indexed: row 2, col 0)\nconsole.log('Writing to cell:', cellAddr);\n\nws[cellAddr] = { t: 's', v: memoText };\n\n// Update sheet range if needed\nconst range = XLSX.utils.decode_range(ws['!ref'] || 'A1:A1');\nif (range.e.r < 2) range.e.r = 2;\nws['!ref'] = XLSX.utils.encode_range(range);\n\n// Write back\nXLSX.writeFile(wb, filePath);\nconsole.log('Done. File saved.');\n\n// Verify\nconst wb2 = XLSX.readFile(filePath);\nconst ws2 = wb2.Sheets['CEOCFO Recommendations'];\nconsole.log('\\nVerification:');\nconsole.log('A1 still exists:', !!ws2['A1']);\nconsole.log('A2 still:', ws2['A2'] ? ws2['A2'].v : '(empty)');\nconsole.log('A3 first 200 chars:', ws2['A3'] ? ws2['A3'].v.substring(0, 200) : '(empty)');\n```\n\nSave as write_memo.js in C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/ and run with node. Return the complete output including verification results."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01AA9ojZuwJMMJXk9Ubr9xqc","session_id":"d2abd3ed-573c-41f0-9505-cb2e0fcd9d65","uuid":"8ae4310d-3333-49d0-a6ff-c61d85169b49","timestamp":"2026-03-22T18:53:15.855Z"}
